It's called Operation
Underground Railroad,

00:35:13.590 --> 00:35:15.140
and it deals with
human trafficking.

00:35:15.140 --> 00:35:16.890
And this group goes
in, and they save kids

00:35:16.890 --> 00:35:19.140
from human trafficking
and slavery.

00:35:19.140 --> 00:35:21.150
And it's a huge issue
today that a lot of us

00:35:21.150 --> 00:35:23.240
don't like to talk
about, and it's amazing.

00:35:23.240 --> 00:35:24.080
It saves lives.

00:35:24.080 --> 00:35:26.340
So you can click the
upper-right-hand corner

00:35:26.340 --> 00:35:28.390
